casebody.data:
Tatyana E. DREVALEVA, Petitioner,
v.
APPELLATE DIVISION OF THE SUPERIOR COURT OF CALIFORNIA, SAN MATEO COUNTY, et al. No. 19-6631 Supreme Court of the United States. January 13, 2020

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeal of California, First Appellate District dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
